<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <%include ./common/header.ejs%>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%=baseUrl%>/css/page/m/sign.css"/>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        window.global = window.global || {};
        global.host = {
            m: "http://<%=host.m%>"
        };
    </script>
    <script src="<%=baseUrl%>/js/m/lib/IB_require.js" async="true" defer data-main="<%=baseUrl%>/js/m/page/IB_sign.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<%include ./common/bodyHeader.ejs%>
<div class="main">
    <div class="register-phone sign-area">
        <div class="sign-line input-area">
            <i class="icon-phone"></i><input type="tel" class="phone input-sign" placeholder="请输入常用手机号码"/>
            <span class="input-error">请输入11位大陆手机号码</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sign-line input-area">
            <i class="icon-vcode"></i>
            <input type="text" class="reg-code-machine  input-sign" placeholder="请输入图形验证码"/>
            <img src="/vcode/create?time=<%=(+new Date)%>" alt="" class="machine-code">
            <span class="btn-refresh"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="sign-line input-area">
            <i class="icon-code"></i><input type="tel" class="code input-sign" placeholder="请输入验证码"/> <button class="btn-sendCode btn">免费获取验证码</button><button class="btn-resendCode">60秒后重试</button>
        </div>
        <div class="sign-line input-area">
            <i class="icon-pwd"></i><input type="password" class="password input-sign" placeholder="请输入6-20位的密码"/>
            <span class="input-error">6-20位密码</span>
        </div>
        <div class="notice">
            点击注册,即代表您已阅读并同意实习鸟<a href="/public/static/m/userProtocol_mobi.html" target="_blank">《用户协议》</a>和<a href="/public/static/m/privacyPolicy_mobi.html"  target="_blank">《隐私政策》</a>。
        </div>
        <div class="sign-line btn-area">
           <button class="btn-register btn-phone btn">注&nbsp;&nbsp;册</button>
        </div>
        <div class="tac notice">
            已有账号？<a href="/login?forward=<%=forward%>">立即登录</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="register-bottom">
        此注册操作适用于有“找实习”需求的对象，若您有“招实习”的需求，请电脑登录<a href="http://www.internbird.com">www.internbird.com</a>注册账号并验证企业信息
    </div>
</div>
<div class="popTips animation"></div>
<%include ./common/footer.ejs%>
</body>
</html>